{"tid":1060627,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發咗幾日】Halo:MCC出pc版","createTime":"2019-03-14T00:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T01:01:58.000Z","uid":203592,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5b842a03757fe9e25435572b88c9aea79be4477f","tid":1060627,"uid":203592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T00:28:36.000Z","msg":"　　在 Xbox One 上，只要擁有《最後一戰：士官長合輯》的玩家都能遊玩《最後一戰：瑞曲之戰》的多人遊戲，包括 Forge 和劇院，而戰役和槍林彈雨則為 DLC。但有訂閱 Xbox Game Pass 的玩家則可以在合輯中玩到完整的《最後一戰：瑞曲之戰》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　本作在 PC 上的釋出方式不同。PC 版的《最後一戰：士官長合輯》將分階段推出，每款遊戲都會逐漸加入。第一個要釋出的遊戲將是《最後一戰：瑞曲之戰》（包括戰役、多人遊戲和槍林彈雨），其餘的遊戲將按時間順序推出，因此順序為《最後一戰：復刻版》、《最後一戰 2》、《最後一戰 3》、《最後一戰 3：ODST》（戰役），然後是《最後一戰 4》。每款遊戲都可以在合輯內單獨購買。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　《最後一戰：士官長合輯》的 PC 版本正在由兩個英國工作室開發，正是總部位於倫敦的 Splash Damage，也在為微軟開發《戰爭機器》作品，以及最近協助製作《除暴戰警 3》且總部位於丹地的 Ruffian<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2019-03-12-halo-the-master-chief-collection-confirmed-for-pc-and-its-coming-to-steam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurogamer.net%2Farticles%2F2019-03-12-halo-the-master-chief-collection-confirmed-for-pc-and-its-coming-to-steam&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrejOHetkdf0TruP2VOJ8R9E%3D&h=9cfb05fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2019-03-12-halo-the-master-chief-collection-confirmed-for-pc-and-its-coming-to-steam</a>"},{"pid":"964cc4e3403e57e59953f5fba72d86c0c33bb86f","tid":1060627,"uid":30092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"等買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望第2集操控有改善"},{"pid":"47666aa842a15c7a58bef3a62b56de4ea2be6bbb","tid":1060627,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"玩第2集已經係10年前既事"},{"pid":"b013683c7832943b5f188392474f6a34245ca49c","tid":1060627,"uid":203592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T04:15:21.000Z","msg":"玩1，2，3，reac